=== NOTE: THESE INSTRUCTIONS ARE NOT COMPLETE. I DO NOT YET CONSIDER KIKI TO
=== BE INSTALLABLE, DOCUMENTATION IS INCOMPLETE AT THIS STAGE

1) Make Kiki htdocs available as /kiki/

Edit config/htaccess and adjust to match your Kiki install path.

Then place the contents in your VirtualHost directive.

2) Directly under your document root, create debug.txt writeable to Apache.

cd /www/example.com
touch debug.txt && chgrp www-data debug.txt && chmod 660 debug.txt

3) Facebook Connect

The canvas root for your Kiki application will be:

http://example.com/kiki/facebook-xd/

Your callback URL is:

http://example.com/kiki/facebook-callback.php

4) Twitter Connect

Your callback URL is:

http://example.com/kiki/twitter-callback.php
